Kali's dotfiles
===============

uses dotfiles -- http://pypi.python.org/pypi/dotfiles/

$ git clone https://github.com/kalikaneko/dotfiles Dotfiles
$ dotfiles --sync

debian vim support
------------------
$ sudo apt-get install vim-nox  # with python support

vim submodule
-------------
git submodule init
git submodule update
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle

unicode support
----------------
I always spend more than needed setting a CJK font for my prompt :(
DO *not* forget to dpkg-reconfigure locales ;)
